title: hOMe Design Plans - Build Your Own Tiny House!
description:
This torrent includes:
-Architectual Plans
-4 Peice DVD set detailing exactly how to go about doing the tiny house build step by step
-Sketchup File of the House and the construction
-Materials List
-Short video telling you how to read the plans

I've uploaded this torrent because I know that many of us who are interested in going tiny, also have tight bugets. 
This will save you an extra $300 hopefully getting you closer to doing you build. If you actually end up doing the build,
I strongly encourage you to support the people that put these plans together. See the http://tinyhousebuild.com/
Seed, Share, Care. 

Good luck on the build!!
